Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.54,0:00:04.81,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,In the latter half of the\NTwentieth Century,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.91,0:00:07.81,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,rapid advancements in technology\Nat last resulted
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.92,0:00:10.91,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,in the development of artificial\Nsubstitutes for human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.39,0:00:15.88,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,A synthesis of mechatronics, artificial\Nintelligence, and biotechnology,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:21.05,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,they freed people from all\Nkinds of menial labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:29.59,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,People called these symbols of the era,\N"Boomers, assemblers of prosperity."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:08.37,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,People all hold more love and dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.71,0:01:15.24,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,than they can hold\Nwith both hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:21.98,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,and paint those dreams\Nfor tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.09,0:01:28.83,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,while entrusting the future to a\Nnew-falling star.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.93,0:01:34.89,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go step by step
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.57,0:01:42.27,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,on your own two legs,\Nwithout stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:48.94,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,before everything your arms\Ntouch transforms into phantasms
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.05,0:01:54.65,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,you can approach those dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:02:01.42,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Now begins the unending dream
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:07.90,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,when you search for yourself, sleeping\Nin the depths of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:13.17,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Now begins the unending journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:21.01,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Fix your sights on a faraway time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:56.41,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:59.18,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Bogarde, why don't you join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.35,0:03:00.48,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut that out, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:02.59,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg your pardon, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:06.92,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Under Article 0012 of the Regulations,\NI cannot leave this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.76,0:03:11.32,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,So long. Good night,\NBogarde.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:12.97,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night. \NTake care, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:15.66,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Mike, Ellie, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.48,0:03:31.65,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a No-Parking Zone. Please\Nmove your vehicle at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:38.65,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do not move within fifteen seconds,\Nthe Police will be notified.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.81,0:04:30.54,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,AD Police, AD Police,\Nthis is Glory Ba...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:33.38,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,A bank robbery involving powered\Nsuits is in progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:35.81,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,The scene is Glory Bank,\Nin the Kabuto Area.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:37.35,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,All personnel, check\Nyour equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:41.35,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,A bank robbery is in progress at\Nthe Kabuto Area Glory Bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:43.25,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,All personnel, check\Nyour equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:55.63,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,You're completely surrounded! Come\Nout of those powered suits quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:06.63,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll count to three! If you don't come out\Nby then, we're coming in after you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:09.54,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:12.51,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:23.58,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.40,0:06:30.80,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:45.71,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Scatter! Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.85,0:06:51.84,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:06:58.85,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not one of\Nour choppers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:06:59.46,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:16.57,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Damage report! Where\Nare our choppers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.31,0:07:19.04,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,No way those guys\Nwere amateurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:28.95,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give us permission to assemble\Na special mobile suit team!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:32.28,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,We're up against an outfit with\Nsome serious military suits!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:35.45,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,With our current equipment, we're\Njust throwing our lives away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:39.99,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening, Chief? The way things\Nare now, we can't do our job!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:42.76,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you're saying, but\Nit just makes my life difficult!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.07,0:07:46.37,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Employing the heavy mobile force is an\Nextremely difficult decision to make
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:49.60,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,when you consider the potential\Nfor civilian casualties, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:53.68,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,We know that! That's why we\Nneed the Diet's approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:57.01,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Please meet with the Diet, so we can use\Nthe heavy equipment without delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:07:59.31,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:02.85,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,But, complaints from citizens\Nhave been heavy lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:05.05,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's something\Nwe can't ignore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:09.46,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your job as Special Police to find\Nsome way to catch these criminals
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.56,0:08:12.05,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,without using the\Nheavy equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:21.80,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:34.55,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, AD Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:39.45,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, can be one of the elite! Join\NAD Police, for youthful adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:42.31,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(367.875,68)}AD Police now recruiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:57.51,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it with the\Nnew Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:09:00.34,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,He's some corporate retiree they\Nappointed so he could earn
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:04.08,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,his retirement pay.\NThey think AD Police is a cash cow, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:06.98,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous. He'll ruin the good\Nname of the Advanced Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:10.55,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like a refill\Non your coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:15.82,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I tell you, AD Police's\Nfuture is shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:19.26,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, about that\Nbank robbery...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:25.54,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:29.30,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Oh, she's\Ndone it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:35.85,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,There's just no end to the breakdowns\Non this built-in coffee-maker model.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:40.14,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have someone clean\Nthis up right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:42.88,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a real problem\Nfor me, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:47.46,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, a hot dog I ate\Nrecently had a spoon in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:49.53,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because even though they\Nlook like human beings
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:53.83,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,they've got no more brains\Nthan an orangutan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:55.87,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I tell ya, there's Boomers\Neverywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:57.93,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the labor shortage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:10:00.20,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear these cheap Boomers\Nare selling like hotcakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.54,0:10:03.57,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,So will there eventually be nothing\Nbut Boomers in Mega Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:12.27,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,We, AD Police, are the Special\NFelony Crimes Elite Team
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.39,0:10:16.08,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,but almost all crime in this town\Nis connected with Boomers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.19,0:10:21.86,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,The Normal Police try to stick us\Nwith writing tickets for them,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.96,0:10:24.09,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,and the bureaucrats,\Nafraid of complaints
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:26.50,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,treat us like we're\Na nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:29.23,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,And to top it off, there's\Nthis new Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:37.74,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you prefer to try calling\Non the Knight Sabers?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.65,0:10:43.58,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,The Knight Sabers...You know, I haven't\Nheard anything about them lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.75,0:10:44.98,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on\Nwith them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.15,0:10:46.55,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Those mercenaries?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.89,0:10:56.59,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Where might a person go
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.70,0:11:02.33,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of streetlights
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:08.34,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,And lots of dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:13.81,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't time stop\Nitself for me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.91,0:11:19.98,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the way it is now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:25.79,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,The days when we laughed\Nside by side
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:31.52,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Are all so far away
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:37.03,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch me, oh, catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:43.08,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm drifting away in\Nthe dead of night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:48.44,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch me...Warm\Nmy closed heart
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.55,0:11:57.98,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,In the palm of your\Nhand, always.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:07.93,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! The bigshots\Nall split.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:12.56,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Priss, babe! That was good! very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:12.56,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:14.67,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,You were excellent, Priss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:15.81,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:18.81,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the big guys are always\Nbusy with something,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:21.38,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,but it seemed as though they really\Nwanted to hear the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:22.21,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:25.44,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh. Didn't I tell\Nyou not to worry?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:27.99,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,We can begin preparations for recording\Nas early as tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:33.45,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Re...Recording? The...The pro\Ndebut I've dreamed of?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:37.82,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Your songs will be\Nall over Mega Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:40.99,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,M...My songs...\NMy songs...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.37,0:12:46.20,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that that's settled, let's continue this\Ndiscussion at my place, just you and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:50.74,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.68,0:12:55.37,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Pr...Priss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:13:03.82,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,My songs are gonna get recorded!\NAll right! All Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:28.47,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.31,0:13:34.01,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Omni's going up! Does\Nsomeone have info on them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:40.58,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Nene's tip about Omni's involvement\Nin developing a new AI was dead on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.39,0:13:47.35,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes? Oh, Omni? Yes, I definitely\Nthink it's going up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:50.49,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty? Why, certainly, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.50,0:13:57.50,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also buying Omni...so go up, go\Nup...and I'll never stop laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:06.21,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,It really was a good idea\Nfor me to change jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:23.50,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your Boomer peppy? If he's getting\Nrun down, then he needs cyber-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:28.84,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Super-power your Boomer. Revive\Nhim instantly, with cyber-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.91,0:14:38.31,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have you two been listening\Nto what I've been saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:41.08,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,My songs...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.12,0:14:45.39,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Essex is on\Nthe move...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:48.15,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.06,0:14:52.46,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Nene? Want\Nanother beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:56.12,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you drink too much. If you strip\Nagain, I won't be responsible for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.83,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's going to strip?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:02.44,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Strip? Did someone\Nsay strip?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.61,0:15:04.51,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's going to strip?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:10.45,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this isn't the planned M&A!\NI can't let them get away with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:12.17,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,You're money-crazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:15.08,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,You got some nerve talking about\Nme, Little Miss Cyberpunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.25,0:15:17.48,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,You only hear me when\NI'm insulting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:20.42,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so interesting about working\Nfor a securities firm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:26.26,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm making money with my brain now.\NNo more sweaty aerobics for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.37,0:15:30.73,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Priss, when you get the money from\Nthe sales of your CD, give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:32.77,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll double it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.71,0:15:35.40,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.97,0:15:40.88,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,All you two think about are yourselves!\NAren't you concerned about Sylia?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:41.81,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Sylia?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:43.35,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Sylia?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.39,0:15:46.31,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,We apologize for the\Ninconvenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.22,0:15:49.19,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,When did they start\Nbuilding here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.35,0:15:51.05,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Some time ago. You\Ndidn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:52.49,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,No. And Sylia?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:54.46,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.17,0:16:03.23,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what're we\Ngonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:04.27,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,"What're we gonna do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:05.33,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:07.30,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,About Sylia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.47,0:16:09.67,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably gone to\Nsee Mackie, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:12.61,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he in Germany? He took off\Nto study there all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:14.21,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,You two sure\Nare carefree.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:16.64,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're that worried,\Nlook for her yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:18.24,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in AD Police,\Nafter all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:22.65,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,AD Police can't be relied upon! \NThat's why the Knight Sabers are necessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:25.35,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go get those powered-suit\Nbank robbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.52,0:16:28.96,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like such barbaric things.\NFor one thing, we won't get any money from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:31.96,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I can't get hurt\Nbefore my debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:34.39,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,And you don't care what happens\Nto the Knight Sabers?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.13,0:16:38.10,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,The Knight Sabers...I am kind\Nof nostalgic about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.27,0:16:39.36,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,No...Nostalgic?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:40.77,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were good\Ntimes, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:42.93,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you refer to them\Nin the past tense?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.68,0:16:53.81,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I never thought that the Knight\NSabers would ever break up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:35.22,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, around 8:30 P.M., another\Nbank was assaulted
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:38.23,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,by a gang wearing military\Nmobile suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.33,0:17:41.70,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,This incident occurred out in the open,\Nin the busy Fourth District
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:46.63,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,and by the time AD Police arrived, the\Ngang had vanished without a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:49.54,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,AD Police still have no leads as\Nto the gang's true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:54.37,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless, public outcry against AD\NPolice's unreliability is growing,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:56.91,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,and speculation is that the organization\Nitself will be re-examined.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:18:00.51,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,How AD Police got to\Nbe like this will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.09,0:18:05.95,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you sit and watch that so\Ncalmly? Aren't you insulted?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:10.79,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point? We can't take\Ndown mobile suits like those.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:13.99,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have any pride\Nin being AD Police?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:16.36,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Dying with your boots\Non isn't very trendy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:18.46,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you can't spend your\Nown insurance money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:21.63,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some\Nway with words.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:25.57,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the Police have gone\Nbad in this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:30.38,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Daley, let's go work off some\Nstress at the shooting range!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:33.34,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.13,0:18:55.04,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to do it. The boss seems\Nto be in bed with a game-maker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.21,0:18:56.54,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:18:59.27,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you, Nene.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:01.81,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you gonna\Nkill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.90,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,After I went to the trouble of digging up\Nthe data on those powered suits?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:14.58,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:18.16,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,This is as close as they get. Perhaps\Nthey've been modified.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:27.83,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,The EC was developing a prototype suit\Nfor close combat three years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:32.00,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,but when faults were identified during\Nthe testing stage, development halted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.34,0:19:33.44,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, officially.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:34.97,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Officially?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.81,0:19:38.30,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,This is as far as the AD\NPolice Databank goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:40.64,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's probably more\Nto it, right, Nene?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.29,0:19:47.42,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a coupon good for three days'\Nworth of free desserts at Scirocco?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:52.19,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,According to another source, there\Nis data which indicates
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:55.13,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,that a European mercenary outfit\Nemployed this type of suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:56.59,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,A mercenary outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:05.31,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Which database did\Nyou pull this from?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.48,0:20:07.47,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Neo-NATO's Top Secret Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.65,0:20:09.61,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,There'd be an international incident\Nif anyone found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:14.88,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,The illegal Army...South America,\Nthe Middle East, Southeast Asia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.99,0:20:16.21,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are such professional\Nwarmongers
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:19.45,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,playing "Gangsters and Terrorists'\Nin Mega Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:23.55,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe they're in\Nit just for the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:24.39,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,But look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:26.93,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently their leader,\None Col. Lando,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:29.43,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,was killed in action a year ago, in\Nan operation in the Philippines.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:37.13,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.24,0:20:41.64,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Word had it that a big Japanese concern\Nwas backing a mercenary outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.75,0:20:43.68,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,But the operation\Nwent awry,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:46.05,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,and nearly the entire unit was\Nsupposedly wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:48.38,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm beginning to get\Nthe picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.99,0:20:52.05,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,But we probably can't do\Nanything to stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:56.52,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up! AD Police\Nis all there is now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:27.35,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, no doubt about it.\NWell done, Col. Lando.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.73,0:21:28.21,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.36,0:21:32.56,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,It does indeed appear to be one of\Nthe components of the new AI.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.66,0:21:36.19,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,But, by itself, it\Nis meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:41.36,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the last two components appears\Nto be at Zone Corporation Labs
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.47,0:21:43.46,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,but we do not know the\Nlocation of the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.64,0:21:50.01,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Get them, whatever it takes. This AI is\Nabsolutely essential to our project.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.92,0:21:51.31,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.15,0:21:54.64,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop saluting, Lando.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.75,0:21:59.09,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not your commander anymore,\NI am your comrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.41,0:22:25.54,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...there you are...\NNow I've got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.09,0:22:35.53,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what's the use? I can't rely on AD\NPolice, I can't get a hold of Sylia,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.63,0:22:37.12,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,and I can't even\Nbeat this game!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.17,0:22:42.15,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.33,0:22:43.36,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Sylia!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.84,0:22:46.67,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Where've you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:50.47,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Here and there...Been renovating\Nthe shop, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.57,0:22:51.87,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,How are Priss\Nand Linna?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.04,0:22:54.17,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they're just peachy!\NLet me tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.11,0:22:58.88,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm currently staying nearby,\Nat the Imperial Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.98,0:23:02.94,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if you'd get the others and\Ncome up to my room this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.05,0:23:05.52,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I've something important to\Ndiscuss with all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.69,0:23:07.02,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Some..Something important?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.73,0:23:10.85,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have a feast laid\Nout for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:13.65,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Sylia...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.57,0:23:23.10,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the\Nfancy food?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.14,0:23:25.40,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not normal, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.51,0:23:28.03,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's our\Nlast supper!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:36.15,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you? Hurry up\Nand eat, so we can start our talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.32,0:23:38.05,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Sylia...about\Nthis "talk"...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.22,0:23:42.06,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to relax without at least\Nhearing what this talk is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.23,0:23:43.25,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.43,0:23:46.33,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...well, there's nothing\Nfor it, I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.43,0:23:49.09,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd really wanted to discuss this after\Ndinner, in a leisurely fashion, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.90,0:23:53.63,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.40,0:23:53.63,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,-No! I won't hear of us breaking up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.64,0:23:57.63,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Nene.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.74,0:24:01.11,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,We understood from the outset that\Nthis would happen someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.28,0:24:07.24,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,But...But I like the work we\Ndo as the Knight Sabers!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.35,0:24:10.32,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, hold on a second,\Nwould you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.82,0:24:14.92,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to say another word,\NSylia. I'm already resigned to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.89,0:24:18.92,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,If Priss and Linna quit,\NI'll do it alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.10,0:24:24.03,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't put it like that. Fact is, a\Npro debut was always my dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.13,0:24:26.40,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I'm going to be busy\Nonce it happens, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.57,0:24:32.67,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, me too. I can manage it, sure,\Nsay, when the market's closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.84,0:24:37.18,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Sylia, I'm begging you! \NStop the Knight Sabers from breaking up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.65,0:24:48.09,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered what you were talking about!\NIs that what you were thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.39,0:24:52.49,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're not going to\Ntalk about breaking up?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.66,0:24:56.50,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we're not going to break\Nup, you silly girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.30,0:24:58.96,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, that something important...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.14,0:25:01.80,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the discussion of our\Nnext job, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.91,0:25:05.77,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,An awful lot of offers have accumulated\Nduring our brief vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.88,0:25:08.31,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,And since the equipment upgrades finally\Nseem to be finished as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.41,0:25:14.15,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,...I thought it was time to start\Nup again...not break up!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.82,0:25:19.02,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Then all my worrying\Nwas for nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.19,0:25:20.28,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Nene!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.46,0:25:22.95,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you think that the Knight\NSabers would disband, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.13,0:25:25.93,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Priss, your pro\Ndebut is set, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.10,0:25:27.93,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, uh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.67,0:25:31.33,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Linna, you're working hard at your\Nsecurities firm, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.67,0:25:34.16,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,How about buying a\Nfew shares, Sylia?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.01,0:25:39.07,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk about that later, when we have\Nmore time. But right now, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.24,0:25:40.34,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind if I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.55,0:25:50.61,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,There seems little doubt that the bank\Nrobbers currently plaguing the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.72,0:25:54.42,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,...are the mercenary outfit known\Nas the illegal Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.53,0:26:00.12,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,But the strange thing is, it's a matter of\Nrecord that their leader, Col. Lando...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.23,0:26:06.60,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,...was killed some years ago, along with\Nnearly all his men, in a failed operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.44,0:26:16.35,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I found out this much just by using\NAD Police's computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.51,0:26:18.14,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrific, Nene.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.32,0:26:22.05,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, with you gone, and the Knight\NSabers seemingly breaking up...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.15,0:26:24.59,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,...I figured that AD Police would have\Nto take our place, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.76,0:26:26.92,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you stop talking\Nabout breaking up!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.09,0:26:28.52,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.69,0:26:34.03,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if we consider this data, then just\Nwho is causing all the fuss now?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.63,0:26:38.29,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the question. Some members\Nmight possibly have survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.77,0:26:40.46,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,And they're trying\Nto take revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.57,0:26:44.23,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,...on the Japanese corporation\Nthat sent them to destruction?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.41,0:26:48.47,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,But all they've done\Nso far is rob banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.65,0:26:50.34,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't seem\Nto be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.45,0:26:54.21,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact is, our client this time\Nout is Zone Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.72,0:26:58.75,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I know Zone...they make Boomer\Nbrains. What's the connection?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.22,0:27:03.13,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,This is one component of the special\NAI which Zone Corporation...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.23,0:27:05.20,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,...secretly developed for\Na new type of Boomer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.53,0:27:10.47,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Zone hasn't told the media, but the\Nillegals stole this component...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.57,0:27:14.13,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,...from Glory Bank, together with\N30 billion in gold bullion.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.01,0:27:16.37,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen\Nanything like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.14,0:27:20.67,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't announce anything because\Nof corporate security concerns.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.78,0:27:24.24,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, just the one component\Nis of no use by itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.35,0:27:28.94,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,The AI's faculties can only be realized\Nif all four components are assembled.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.72,0:27:33.12,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,So the first two were\Nat Glory and Omni?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.29,0:27:36.66,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. In short, they're using the\Nmoney as a smokescreen.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.76,0:27:39.99,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,But their real objective is the\Nfour components of this AI.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.10,0:27:42.53,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Our job is to protect\Nthe remaining two.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.70,0:27:44.06,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.23,0:27:47.29,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,The bait has already been laid out. We\Nmay get a nibble any time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.56,0:28:06.54,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,This makes three.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.83,0:28:15.96,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there,\Nmercenaries!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.07,0:28:18.13,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Surrender! Resistance\Nis useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.44,0:28:20.49,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Not the flies again...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.00,0:28:24.57,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw down your\Nweapons at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.91,0:28:29.17,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.69,0:28:42.28,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys won't be pushing\Nanyone around anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.86,0:28:43.69,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.66,0:28:45.49,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.86,0:28:49.89,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,A hornet among\Nthe flies...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.87,0:28:54.80,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for the pride\Nof AD Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.04,0:29:01.03,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interfere!\NI'll take him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.21,0:29:03.30,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon doesn't stand a chance\Nagainst a suit like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.48,0:29:04.50,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Let him do it his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.15,0:29:11.71,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.46,0:29:16.12,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.83,0:29:20.39,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry 'bout that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.63,0:29:23.29,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.63,0:29:26.66,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Victory is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.65,0:29:38.67,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on! We're getting\Nout of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.45,0:29:43.55,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, sir! \NPlease, just leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.72,0:29:47.16,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you die!\NI'm gonna save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.60,0:30:00.59,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back\Nfrom the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.37,0:30:03.70,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,It's humiliating, but\Nhe beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.87,0:30:07.87,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,You take it easy for a while.\NI'll explain it to the Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.71,0:30:13.45,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting that aside, why did they steal\Na component of a research project?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.55,0:30:15.61,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem like they\Nwere after money.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.79,0:30:19.42,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,But it amounts to the same thing.\NAfter all, they can convert it into money.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.26,0:30:24.89,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not Lando's style. He\Nmust be after something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.10,0:30:34.00,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the warriors who\Nhave been chosen...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.10,0:30:37.94,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,...to bring forth a new order\Nupon the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.28,0:30:41.27,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,This war you fight\Nis a holy war.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.93,0:31:02.56,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is changing. The history of\Nfoolish old humankind is ending...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.67,0:31:05.50,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,...and we, the chosen,\Nwill purify the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.54,0:31:14.84,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.48,0:31:18.92,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it great? You'll look terrific\Nwhen you put it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.25,0:31:22.18,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and here's your\Nsheet music.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.79,0:31:26.31,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? This ain't\Nmy song.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.89,0:31:31.38,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that song will be a coupling\Nsong and this is the main one.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.23,0:31:36.36,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,It's by Fuyumoto, the popular idol\Nhitmaker, so it can't miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.53,0:31:38.43,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I...Idol?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.44,0:31:45.10,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, leave everything to me,\Nand I won't steer you wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.28,0:31:46.44,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.58,0:31:49.91,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to be\Nembarrassed about.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.61,0:31:55.95,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we're already one\Nflesh, inseparable.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.12,0:31:59.78,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,That does it! You got some nerve,\Nthinking I'll hold still for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.89,0:32:02.79,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'll become an\Nidol, you son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.16,0:32:12.12,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh...This is a temporary\Nthing, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.67,0:32:19.60,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? There's...no need to talk like\Nthat...what? Sell out? Uh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.28,0:32:29.15,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You've lost 500,000? Just\Nlike me, huh? Oh, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.79,0:32:31.52,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Omni's really taken\Na nosedive.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.69,0:32:33.59,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of that bank\Nrobbery, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.56,0:32:42.56,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes, well, it's...Damn the illegal\NArmy! I've had it up to here!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.91,0:32:43.54,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(381.375,232)}Resignation
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.70,0:32:45.69,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.87,0:32:46.49,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.40,0:32:49.80,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I resign, effective\Nimmediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.40,0:33:21.20,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,The illegal Army should presently be\Nheading for Stephan Laboratories...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.30,0:33:23.03,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,...thanks to the false information\NI've planted.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.74,0:33:26.40,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Knight Sabers are Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.28,0:35:07.74,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.68,0:35:14.62,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! It's a trap!\NPull out!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.78,0:35:18.19,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,We...we can't, sir! Our escape\Nroute is completely sealed off!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.86,0:35:21.12,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter! We'll just\Ngo up to the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.24,0:35:34.76,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Knight Sabers...Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.34,0:35:38.67,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just do as you\Nplease in this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.84,0:35:41.24,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten a bit cocky,\Nhaven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.84,0:35:42.64,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.48,0:36:51.97,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you give me\Nthe last component?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.42,0:36:54.11,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! What can you do, alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.28,0:36:58.58,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,When the battle is joined, nobody\Nstands in our way and lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.37,0:37:14.43,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,You babes are\Npretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.44,0:37:20.00,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Priss, Nene, we'll attack him\Nfrom three sides, all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.18,0:37:21.14,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.38,0:37:25.11,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.68,0:37:29.48,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave them to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.46,0:37:41.36,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Got 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.53,0:37:44.09,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Without their suits, they're\Njust cheap Boomers.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.81,0:37:54.97,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.56,0:38:08.22,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.76,0:38:11.69,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all for today,\NKnight Sabers!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.33,0:38:15.16,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get off\Nthat easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.63,0:38:16.39,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.31,0:38:29.18,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Stealing the second generation Boomer\NAI under cover of bank robberies...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.28,0:38:31.21,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,...wasn't simply gathering funds\Nor taking revenge, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.01,0:38:33.14,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's their boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.32,0:38:37.79,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Priss!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.89,0:38:44.26,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the illegal Army. I take\Norders from no one!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.09,0:38:47.59,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Release her! You have no\Nhope of winning now!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.13,0:38:51.69,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a soldier of the glorious\Nillegal Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.80,0:38:53.77,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't enough to\Nmake me give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.51,0:38:58.47,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Shove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.52,0:39:08.31,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.35,0:39:13.25,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.19,0:39:18.89,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.20,0:39:28.40,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.95,0:39:40.81,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Give yourself up! Who\Nis your boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.19,0:39:44.08,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,A self-destruct device!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.35,0:39:45.08,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.72,0:39:50.21,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late to start running now!\NI'll destroy everything within 3km!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.39,0:39:52.29,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,One minute to\Ndetonation!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.76,0:39:53.66,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Find the self-destruct device!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.13,0:39:55.10,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.23,0:40:01.33,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you? I'll\Nblow us all away together!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.74,0:40:08.90,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,The illegal Army does\Nnot surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.79,0:40:18.38,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.59,0:40:19.38,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Nene, link up with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.82,0:40:20.91,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Priss!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.26,0:40:23.52,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Synchronize targets, Priss!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.93,0:40:24.92,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.20,0:40:35.14,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all yours, Priss!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.14,0:40:38.47,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,If you miss, it's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.48,0:40:40.57,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.69,0:41:01.96,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good...\Nyou beat us...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.53,0:41:03.66,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,...this time, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.37,0:41:04.99,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.70,0:41:10.26,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a failed Boomer; neither\NBoomer nor human.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.37,0:41:14.21,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,But soon, there will come a world...with\Nneither humans nor Boomers in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.88,0:41:19.78,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,...a dream world, controlled only\Nthrough chaos and terror...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.88,0:41:23.98,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,...if anyone can make\Nit reality, he can...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.04,0:41:42.53,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's still hope\Nfor this town, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.93,0:42:10.13,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's become of\Nyour pro debut?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.33,0:42:13.30,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna write some decent\Nsongs, and go for it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.60,0:42:17.31,Style Asong,,0000,0000,0000,,When the bell rings, showtime's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.37,0:42:15.97,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a call from another record\Ncompany just the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.11,0:42:20.41,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I've also decided to work\Nat another securities firm!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.37,0:42:24.15,Style Asong,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, I've seen my dream's continuation.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.54,0:42:23.01,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say you never even\Nwanted to see money again?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.15,0:42:26.02,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's lovely to watch\Nmoney pile up.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.21,0:42:29.79,Style Asong,,0000,0000,0000,,Today ends, having gone the way I wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.92,0:42:29.02,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are money-crazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.25,0:42:31.39,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that, Little Miss Cyberpunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.85,0:42:37.98,Style Asong,,0000,0000,0000,,And tomorrow, I seek an easygoing dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.52,0:42:32.82,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you quarreling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.36,0:42:36.46,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sylia, these two still haven't learned anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.59,0:42:37.36,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Nene!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.09,0:42:44.39,Style Asong,,0000,0000,0000,,People are dreaming hurriedly
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.73,0:42:42.67,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, do your thing, but don't\Nforget the Knight Sabers.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.27,0:42:57.14,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,and though no voice gets through,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.25,0:43:02.68,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,strangely, I can hear your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.79,0:43:09.49,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,cool eyes, staring just that way
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.59,0:43:12.99,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,cloud the mirror of the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.10,0:43:18.12,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,concealing one's true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.20,0:43:23.26,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,With stardust reflected in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.37,0:43:26.67,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,you embrace freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.78,0:43:30.80,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,and firmly catch your own dream, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.91,0:43:40.98,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Showtime, in a town full of misunderstandings.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.07,0:43:58.87,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, the heart walks a tightrope.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.97,0:44:05.57,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Straining my eyes in the pitch darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.68,0:44:11.28,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,unable to see anything, I seek tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.39,0:44:19.32,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,The bustling town is dancing
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.43,0:44:26.16,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,with a seemingly secret heart, tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.27,0:44:33.11,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,The melody you and I heard is carried
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.21,0:44:38.61,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,on the wind, and surrounds you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.71,0:44:45.52,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensitive cool eyes really know the things
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.62,0:44:50.99,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,that possess eyes which seem to melt ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.09,0:44:59.19,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,With stardust reflected in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.30,0:45:02.63,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,you embrace freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.74,0:45:06.70,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,and firmly catch your own heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.81,0:45:16.44,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensitive cool eyes really know the things
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.55,0:45:24.98,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,that possess eyes which seem to melt ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.09,0:45:30.03,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,With stardust reflected in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.13,0:45:33.47,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,you embrace freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.57,0:45:37.63,Style,,0000,0000,0000,,and firmly catch your own heart.
